section.header: Replacement of John H. Chafee Coastal Barrier Resources System map

subsection.text: The map included in the set of maps entitledCoastal Barrier Resources Systemreferred to in section 4(a) of the Coastal Barrier Resources Act(16 U.S.C. 3503(a))and relating to Unit L06 in North Carolina is hereby replaced by another map relating to the same unit entitledJohn H. Chafee Coastal Barrier Resources System Corrected Unit L06and dated ______.

TheSecretary of the Interiorshall keep the replacement map referred to insubsection (a)on file and available for inspection in accordance with section 4(b) of the Coastal Barrier Resources Act(16 U.S.C. 3503(b)).
